sentence: display all flights leaving from toronto to san diego on u s air laying over in washington d c
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.airline_code||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.flight_id||'"', '"'||v6.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_name||'"', '"'||v7.state_code||'"',
 v5.stop_number FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4, flight_stop v5,
 airport_service v6, city v7 
WHERE ((v0.airline_code = 'US') 
AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'TORONTO'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'SAN DIEGO'))) 
AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) AND ((v5.stop_airport = ANY v6.airport_code) 
AND ((v6.city_code = ANY v7.city_code) 
AND ((v7.city_name = 'WASHINGTON') AND (v7.state_code = 'DC'))))))));
